This Script is to take the Automatic Backup of MySQL and System Files on your own system and also on the another system using scp.


How to Use:

1. First of all set up your system to ssh and scp without entring password.
Follow the tutrial to set up ssh loging without password.
http://parveenarora.in/ssh_without_password

2. You will need to edit the script according to the values of your choice.

3. The Use the script in crontab to automate the process.
Follow this tutorial to run the script using crontab.



